# None-Profit Pharceutical crowd sourced

## Original Author: Leo Benkel

## Status: BRAINSTORMING

## Idea

### Description

This would be a non profit company, crowd sourced, pharmaceutical company. 
The goal would be to produce low cost medicine and focus of cures 
instead of medication to keep patient alive to get money out of them.
Having all fund coming from crowd sourcing will allow the entity to be free of corporate influence.

## Use cases

* Cure disease.
* Allow people to be healthy.
